1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,011
Remember the complete method in three lines.

2
00:00:02,961 --> 00:00:07,326
First, delegate work with a concrete output, not a vague topic.

3
00:00:07,326 --> 00:00:13,173
Second, require accessible context and trustworthy feedback before the agent acts independently.

4
00:00:13,173 --> 00:00:17,541
Third, bound permissions and put approval before irreversible actions.

5
00:00:17,541 --> 00:00:25,163
The Task Upgrade Scorecard moves from chat to copilot, supervised agent, and delegated workflow only as those gates become true.

6
00:00:25,163 --> 00:00:27,653
The goal is not maximum autonomy.

7
00:00:27,653 --> 00:00:32,028
It is reliable production with less human handling and no loss of control.

8
00:00:32,028 --> 00:00:42,336
Follow Tiny Agent for practical ways to choose AI tasks, package context, verify results, control risk, and turn one successful delegation into a repeatable workflow.
